== Motivation == 

This is a simple web implementation of the basic 101companies-features, plus 
database persistence and authentication/authorization feaures, using  
the SEAM framework.

== Illustration ==

== Architecture ==

== Usage ==

* '''Requirements:'''
** [[Technology:JBoss|JBoss]]-4.2.x (http://sourceforge.net/projects/jboss/files/JBoss/JBoss-4.2.3.GA)
** [[Technology:Eclipse]]
* '''Deployment:'''
** Import the seam project as a java project into eclipse.
** change the build.properties located in the projects base folder. The ''jboss.home''-property must refer to your JBoss location:  ''jboss.home = <your jboss location>''
** run the seam project as ant build in eclipse.
* '''Access:'''
** start a web-browser
** go to: http://localhost:8080/seam
** Access the system with user ''admin'' (pw:''admin''). You can also access the system with user ''user'' (pw: ''user'') but then the cut salaries method is blocked.

